  <summary date="2019-05-09T04:00:00Z" status="Introduced in House">Safer Occupancy Furniture Flammability Act or SOFFAThis bill adopts the California flammability standard as the federal standard for upholstered furniture. To meet the standard, the upholstered furniture must past a specific test of the materials' ability to resist smoldering when a heat source is applied.</summary>
